#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:296
msgid ""
"|indicatorNonRemovable| to identify layers that are :ref:`required "
"<project_layer_capabilities>` in the project, hence non removable"
msgstr ""
"|indicatorNonRemovable| per identificare i layer che sono :ref:`required "
"<project_layer_capabilities>` nel progetto, quindi non rimovibili"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:298
msgid ""
"|indicatorEmbedded| to identify an :ref:`embedded group or layer "
